<section>
  <p class="title" data-section-title>
    <a href="#" class="long">I have money in my wallet but the system won't let me open a position, it
      says "NO RESERVE"? <i></i></a></p>

  <div class="content" data-section-content>
    <p>When you trade on margin you need to take liquidity from liquidity providers. If there is no
      liquidity provider available your order status says "no reserve active" which means that the order
      will be executed as soon as there is liquidity available.</p>
  </div>
</section>
<section>
  <p class="title" data-section-title>
    <a href="#">I would like to just buy or sell like on any other exchanges, what should I do?
      <i></i></a></p>

  <div class="content" data-section-content>
    <p>You can open an "Exchange" account and use the "Exchange" tab of Bitfinex.</p>
  </div>
</section>
<section>
  <p class="title" data-section-title>
    <a href="#">I am a long term Bitcoin/Litecoin holder, what type of account suits me the best? <i></i></a>
