<section>
  <p class="title" data-section-title><a href="#">What is a "Hidden order"? <i></i></a></p>

  <div class="content" data-section-content>
    <p>A hidden order is an order which does not appear in the orderbook, and thus doesn't influence other
      market participants. <a href="/pages/fees">See the fees page</a> for minimum size and fee
      applicable.</p>
  </div>
</section>
